quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"Jewe Allah, Ndarahiye ku musozi wa Twuuri Sinayi, ari na wo Navuganiyeko na Musa ukuri kwamye;"
  52,2,"No ku Gitabu ca Qor’ani canditswe;"
  52,3,"No ku Mizingo ihinguwe mu rusato, yuguruye;"
  52,4,"No ku ngoro iri mw’ijuru ryegereye isi, irimwo abamalayika bama bariko barayikikura ku mwanya ku mwanya;"
  52,5,"No kw’ijuru ryegereye isi, rikaba ari na co gisenge cayo;"
  52,6,"No kw’ibahari rizodomekwa rikarurumba ku musi w’umuhero w’isi;"
  52,7,"Ko mu vy’ukuri ibihano vy’Imana yawe Rurema ga Ntumwa y’Imana, bitegerezwa gushikira abagarariji;"
  52,8,"Nta n’uwuzobuza ko nya bihano bibashikira;"
  52,9,"Ku musi ijuru ryasenyutse rigacika ubunywenywe;"
  52,10,"Imisozi na yo igakurwaho, maze ikagenda nka kurya ubona ibicu bigenda!"
  52,11,"Uguhanwa nya guhanwa kuri uwo musi, ni ukw’abahakana ukuri bivuye inyuma;"
  52,12,"Barya bishinga gufyinata mu gutebura kw’idini;"
  52,13,"Umusi rero, abahakanyi basunikiwe mu muriro wa Jahannamu ukuri kwo gusunikirwayo;"
  52,14,"Bazobwirwa n’agashinyaguro n’akantu bati: “Ng’uwo wa muriro mwahora muhakana ko utabaho;"
  52,15,"Mbega none ibi bihano murimwo, ni uburozi canke nta vyo mubona!"
  52,16,"Nimuwinjire muwote rero; mwihangana mutihangana, vyose ni kimwe, ntimurota mutezurirwa mu bihano. Ni ukuri, muhemberwa ivyo mwari mwarakoze kw’isi”."
  52,17,"Mu vy’ukuri abagamburukiramana, bazoba bari mu mirima itotahaye yo mu Bwami bw’ijuru, bari no mu nema zihambaye;"
  52,18,"Akamwemwe kabasya, baryohewe n’inema z’ubwoko bwose bahawe n’Imana yabo Rurema Allah, kandi Imana yabo Rurema Allah Izonabakingira ibihano vy’umuriro ururumba wa Jahannamu;"
  52,19,"Maze babwirwe bati: “Nimurye mwongere munywe n’akayabagu kenshi, burya muhembewe ibikorwa vyiza mwari mwarakoze kw’isi”."
  52,20,"Bazoba rero bicaye ku bitanda bisharije bitondetse neza. Tuzonabatera iteka Tubashingire abakenyezi bo mu Bwami bw’ijuru, barangwa n’ubwiza bw’akataraboneka (Hururayini)."
  52,21,"Na barya bemeye, maze n’uruvyaro rwabo rukabakurikira mu kwemera, Tuzobakurikiza uruvyaro rwabo mu Bwami bw’ijuru, n’aho batazoba bari ku rugezo rw’ibikorwa vyabo, kandi ntituzogabanya na kimwe ku ndishi y’ivyo bakoze. Burya umuntu wese azofatirwa ku vyo yakoze, nta wuzohanirwa icaha c’uwundi."
  52,22,"Hejuru y’inema bazoba barimwo, Tuzobaha ivyamwa n’inyama bitera akayabagu, kuko biri mu bintu bikundwa cane;"
  52,23,"Tuzobaha n’umwuhiro w’inzoga zitaboreza, ibirahuri vy’inzoga bikurakuranwa, bahererekanya hagati yabo mu Bwami bw’ijuru; nya nzoga, nta ho zisa zisana n’izo kw’isi ziyayura umutwe, umuntu agatangura kudedemba avuga ayamuhe yitonganya;"
  52,24,"Bazoba bakikijwe n’imisore myiza, ikurakuranwa mu kubazimana; uyibonye, ku bwiza bwayo wogira ngo ni lulu zikiri aho zaremewe, zitarakorwako n’iminwe y’abantu."
  52,25,"Abari mu Bwami bw’ijuru, bazobazanya hagati yabo, batera inkuru z’ubuzima babanyemwo n’abandi kw’isi;"
  52,26,"Maze bavuge bati: “Mu vy’ukuri, mu buzima twabayeho mu bacu, aho hambere kw’isi, twaratinya Imana yacu Rurema Allah, tukamana impungenge ku bihano vyo ku musi w’izuka;"
  52,27,"Maze Imana Allah Itugirira ubuntu, Iturongora mu nzira yayo, Iraheza Idukingira n’ibihano vy’umwokero wa Jahannamu;"
  52,28,"Mu vy’ukuri n’imbere y’ugukingirwa nya bihano, twahora dutakambira Imana Allah, mu kuyisaba tutayibangikanya, ko Yobidukingira. Mu vy’ukuri, ni Yo Mugiranezamurivyose, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo”."
  52,29,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ibutsa rero abo warungitsweko ukoresheje Qor’ani, kuko guhabwa kwawe ubutumwa n’ubumenyi mw’idini, si vyo vyotuma witwa Senyagara avuga ivyo adafitiye ubumenyi, canke umusazi yakehewe n’ubwenge."
  52,30,"Canke ababangikanyamana boba bavuga bati: “Uwo Muhamadi mwumva, ni umwivuzi w’amazina, tumuteze imisi, mureke urupfu ruramubona!”"
  52,31,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Bishure uti: “Nimurindire urupfu rwanje, nanje mu vy’ukuri ndacarindiriye hamwe na mwe ibihano muzohabwa”."
  52,32,"Ahubwo rero, burya ubwenge bw’ababangikanyamana, bwoba bubategeka kuvuga ijambo ry’igarariza nk’iryo, mu gihe bitarigera bishika ko umuntu yoba senyagara, akaba umwivuzi w’amazina, akaba n’umusazi mu mwanya umwe! Ahubwo rero bo, ni abantu bimonogoje mu kurenga ku mabwirizwa y’Imana Allah."
  52,33,"Ahubwo none, ababangikanyamana boba bavuga ko Muhamadi yarementanije Qor’ani! Ahubwo rero bo, ntibemera namba."
  52,34,"Nivyaba biri nk’ukwo babivuga, nibazane rero amajambo arementanije nka Qor’ani, nibaba ari imvugakuri ko Muhamadi yarementanije Qor’ani."
  52,35,"Mbega ababangikanyamana, boba baremwe n’ubusa ata cabaremye! Canke boba bariremye! Usangwa bataremwe n’ubusa canke ngo bireme, nibamenye rero ko Imana Allah ari Yo Yabaremye, n’uko ari Yo rero, Ikwiye gusengwa Itabangikanywa."
  52,36,"Canke boba bararemye amajuru n’isi muri ubu buryo buhimbaye! Ahubwo rero, ntibemera namba ko bazohanwa."
  52,37,"Canke boba bajejwe ibigega vy’Imana yawe Rurema Allah! Canke boba baganza ibiremwa vy’Imana Allah! Ahubwo rero bo, nta n’ico bishoboje."
  52,38,"Canke boba bafise ingazi burirako ngo bumvirize ihishurwa ry’Imana Allah ko bari mu kuri! Nivyaba biri nk’ukwo babivuga rero, uwavyumvise muri bo, enda rero nyabuna nazane icemeza kigaragara cemeza ko bari mu kuri."
  52,39,"Mbega none, Imana Allah Yarigeneye abana b’abakobwa, Iraheza na mwe Ibagenera abana b’abahungu nk’uko muvyibwira mwihenda!"
  52,40,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ahubwo rero, woba usaba ababangikanyamana impembo kw’irarikiramana ryawe, bigatuma batakwumvira ku kuremerwa n’iyo mpembo ubasaba!"
  52,41,"Canke boba bafise ubumenyi bw’ibinyegejwe ibiremwa, baheza bakabwandika babushikiriza abantu! Baranguha, ubwo bumenyi bw’ibinyegejwe ibiremwa ni ubw’Imana Allah gusa."
  52,42,"Ahubwo bashaka gukoresha urwenge ngo bagirire nabi Intumwa n’abemeramana. Nibamenye rero, ko Imana Allah Izohinyura urwenge rw’abagararije, maze inabi babipfuriza igaruke kuri bo nyene, na kare ngo urucira mukaso rugatwara nyoko."
  52,43,"Canke boba bafise iyindi mana ikwiye gusengwa atari Imana Allah! Nihaninahazwe rero Imana Allah mu buryo burengeye cane ivyo ababangikanyamana bayibangikanya."
  52,44,"Ababangikanyamana no mu gihe bobona igihande c’ijuru kibaguyeko, ntiboretse guhakana, bovuze bati: “Ivyo, ni ibicu gusa vyiyegeranije”."
  52,45,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ababangikanyamana, bareke barendegere gushika igihe bahuye n’umusi wabo w’izuka bazohanirwako;"
  52,46,"Umusi urwenge rwabo ata na kimwe ruzobamarira mu gihe bazoba bari mu bihano vy’Imana Allah; eka mbere bobo, ntibazoronka n’uwubatabara ngo abibakuremwo."
  52,47,"Mu vy’ukuri, abirenganije mu guhakana, barategekanirijwe n’ibihano mu buzima bwo kw’isi, ariko rero abenshi muri bo nta vyo bazi."
  52,48,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ihanganire rero ishikirizabutumwa ku bw’Imana Allah, maze wihanganire n’ibangamira ry’abaguhakana; mu vy’ukuri wewe, Tugushinze ijisho nta kigukorako urakingiwe, uheze uninahaze n’Imana yawe Rurema Allah mu kuyishimagiza mu gihe ugiye gusenga no mu gihe uvyutse;"
  52,49,"Uheze rero no mw’ijoro uyininahaze mu kuyishimagiza mw’isengesho, wongere ugire nk’ukwo nyene mu mutwenzi igihe c’irenga ry’inyenyeri."
